                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Dans les rameaux pleins de soleil.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La rose semble, rajeunie,\nS'accoupler au bouton vermeil ;\nL'oiseau chante plein d'harmonie\nDans les rameaux pleins de soleil."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Sa voix bénit le Dieu de l'âme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Qui, toujours visible au cœur pur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Fait l'aube, paupière de flamme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Pour le ciel, prunelle d'azur !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sa voix bénit le Dieu de l'âme\nQui, toujours visible au cœur pur,\nFait l'aube, paupière de flamme,\nPour le ciel, prunelle d'azur !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Sous les bois, où tout bruit s'émousse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Le faon craintif joue en rêvant ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Dans les verts écrins de la mousse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Luit le scarabée, or vivant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sous les bois, où tout bruit s'émousse,\nLe faon craintif joue en rêvant ;\nDans les verts écrins de la mousse\nLuit le scarabée, or vivant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "La lune au jour est tiède et pâle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Comme un joyeux convalescent ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Tendre, elle ouvre ses yeux d'opale",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "D'où la douceur du ciel descend !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La lune au jour est tiède et pâle\nComme un joyeux convalescent ;\nTendre, elle ouvre ses yeux d'opale\nD'où la douceur du ciel descend !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "La giroflée avec l'abeille",
